---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Miguel Morales | Resume">
   <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <!-- Header -->
      <section class="text-center mb-16">
         <h1
            class="
            text-5xl
            font-bold
            text-rose
            "
            >
            Miguel Morales
         </h1>
         <p
            class="
            mt-4
            text-2xl
            text-mauve
            "
            >
            Software Engineer / Engineering Lead / Game Developer
         </p>
         <p
            class="
            mt-6
            text-white/80
            max-w-3xl
            mx-auto
            leading-relaxed
            "
            >
            Software engineer specializing in Unity/C# and Client Architecture.
            Experienced building and shipping interactive products from concept
            to production. <br><br>I've been in the games industry for over a decade and wore all sorts of hats: game developer, fullstack engineering, technical lead, manager and, more recently, executive.
         </p>
      </section>
      <!-- Skills -->
      <section class="mb-16">
         <h2
            class="
            text-3xl
            font-bold
            text-rose
            mb-6
            "
            >
            Skills
         </h2>
         <div
            class="
            flex
            flex-wrap
            gap-3
            "
            >
            {
            [
            "Unity",
            "C#",
            "Gameplay Programming",
            "Mobile Development",
            "Analytics",
            "Integrations",
            "mySQL",
            "unix",
            "objectiveC",
            "javascript",
            "html",
            "java",
            "php",
            "LiveOps",
            "git",
            "Software Architecture",
            "Engineering Leadership",
            "Mentoring"
            ].map(skill => (
            <span
               class="
               px-4
               py-2
               rounded-full
               bg-purple/30
               border
               border-purple
               "
               >
            {skill}
            </span>
            ))
            }
         </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Experience -->
      <section class="mb-16">
         <h2
            class="
            text-3xl
            font-bold
            text-rose
            mb-6
            "
            >
            Experience
         </h2>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3
               class="
               text-2xl
               font-bold
               "
               >
               VP of Engineering, Engineering Manager, Principal Engineer
            </h3>
            <p
               class="
               text-mauve
               mt-1
               "
               >
               Super Free Games, Inc - San Francisco, CA <i>(2013 - 2024)</i>
            </p>
            <ul
               class="
               mt-5
               space-y-3
               text-white/80
               list-disc
               list-inside
               "
               >
               <li>
                  Founding Engineer of the core systems and process that comprise the infrastructure and products of the company. 
               </li>
               <li>
                  Developed the games themselves, internal tools, liveOps, automation pipelines, release pipelines, analytics, backend, etc.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Joined as a Founding Engineer, became Engineering Lead, Manager and recently and executive position.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Focused on systems architecture, performance optimization and liveOps, as well as mentoring.
               </li>
               <li>
                  The company got acquired on 2021 and once earnout period was over, decided to leave and pursue other interests.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <br>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3
               class="
               text-2xl
               font-bold
               "
               >
               Senior Game Developer
            </h3>
            <p
               class="
               text-mauve
               mt-1
               "
               >
               Visionaria Games, S de RL - Mexico City, Mexico <i>(2011 - 2012)</i>
            </p>
            <ul
               class="
               mt-5
               space-y-3
               text-white/80
               list-disc
               list-inside
               "
               >
               <li>
                  Developed Web Games for educational purposes.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Led a team of 3 engineers and maintained good coding practices, good orchestration schemas and interoperability between client and server(backend)
               </li>
               <li>
                  Mostly worked on client development in ActionScript and native (objectiveC)
               </li>
               <li>
                  Left before a full year to pursue a bigger opportunity.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <br>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3
               class="
               text-2xl
               font-bold
               "
               >
               Fullstack Engineer
            </h3>
            <p
               class="
               text-mauve
               mt-1
               "
               >
               Digital Chocolate - Mexicali, Mexico <i>(2011)</i>
            </p>
            <ul
               class="
               mt-5
               space-y-3
               text-white/80
               list-disc
               list-inside
               "
               >
               <li>
                  Developed tools and ported the Company's Game to the internal Network of the Company
               </li>
               <li>
                  Constant communication with the Helsinki and Barcelona studios for porting and maintenance of the games.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Fullstack development with ActionScript, PhP, Facebook Integrations, Unix, MySQL.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Left before a full year to pursue a different opportunity in my hometown.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <br>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3
               class="
               text-2xl
               font-bold
               "
               >
               Engineer and GameDev
            </h3>
            <p
               class="
               text-mauve
               mt-1
               "
               >
               IkiGaming S. de R.L. - Mexico City, Mexico <i>(2009-2010)</i>
            </p>
            <ul
               class="
               mt-5
               space-y-3
               text-white/80
               list-disc
               list-inside
               "
               >
               <li>
                  Fullstack Development of social games for the Facebook Platform.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Worked mainly on ActionScript, Javascript and PhP
               </li>
               <li>
                  Focused on learning good coding practices and design patterns, as well as performance optimization.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <br>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3
               class="
               text-2xl
               font-bold
               "
               >
               Cofounder and Entrepreneur
            </h3>
            <p
               class="
               text-mauve
               mt-1
               "
               >
               Ignis Nova, S. de R.L. - Mexico City, Mexico <i>(2008-2009)</i>
            </p>
            <ul
               class="
               mt-5
               space-y-3
               text-white/80
               list-disc
               list-inside
               "
               >
               <li>
                  Started a small company to create software with ethical responsibility.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Worked on videogames for rehabilitation, a small social network and networking infrastructure.
               </li>
               <li>
                  Left to pursue my passion of working on videogames.
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
      </section>
      <!-- Education -->
      <section>
         <h2
            class="
            text-3xl
            font-bold
            text-rose
            mb-6
            "
            >
            Education
         </h2>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">
               Bachelors Degree, Computer Science
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">
               Instituto Tecnologico y de Estudios Superiores de Monterrey, Campus Ciudad de Mexico <br><i>(2004 - 2008)</i>
               <br><br>
               Studied Software Engineering and CompSci to pursue my dream of creating videogames.
            </p>
         </div>
      </section>
      <br>
      <br>
      <!-- Personal Interests -->
      <section>
         <h2
            class="
            text-3xl
            font-bold
            text-rose
            mb-6
            "
            >
            Personal Interests
         </h2>
         <div
            class="
            bg-purple/20
            border
            border-purple
            rounded-2xl
            p-6
            "
            >
            <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">
               I love reading and running. Have done multiple marathons and read a lot of about Psychology, Sci-Fi, Philosophy and Programming.
               <br><br>
               I like learning new languages. Currently on Japanese and Korean.
            </p>
         </div>
      </section>
   </main>
</Layout>